metadata.name: GIGGLEMUGZ: Anti-Nuke Trippityz!
metadata.description:
SPIFFEE & TWIZLIT ! Offering greetingZ to your BrAiN ! We Don't Like Nuclear-ArmamentZ! We like Brain-Food! & What IS THIS PLACE?!

!?!!tEe-HeE TeHee-Hee! !?!! ...As sighted innumerable parsecs away hanging' out 'n' gettin' down in sum whackadoo Toony-LooniverZe & subsequently depicted to earthlings by Mr. Face-Head in just 250 Silly-SceneZ, GIGGLEMUGZ are varying arrangements of some very merry-duos of Oddballish, Smiley-Pie crushing, Intergalactoidal-BFFZ ! Suitably named for their Jolly-Zinger attitudes, 'Chickle', 'Spiffee', 'Twizlit' & 'Noische' are in Quick-Command & Hi-Demand!  
   Materializing in slap-happy support of Mr. Face-Head's up & coming 'SPACE-PUNX'...GigglerZ will get the word out between snickerZ 'n' lolligaggin' about their lunar-loony companions who are on the way across the vast sea of stars to the cosmicly-insignificant speck of earth to bring Joy! Come-Along for a LOONG, StrAAAnge DRIP!!!
